flowent - package flowent
This is the main Flowent Java API package.
Flowent - Class in flowent
Flowent is a fluent interface API written for the Java Programming Language.
Flowent() - Constructor for class flowent.Flowent
The standard constructor for the Flowent main class.
Flowent(boolean) - Constructor for class flowent.Flowent
This constructor gives you the option to log everything.
FlowentForLoop - Interface in flowent
FlowentForLoop is an interface that can be utilized to create loops from within the method chain.
FlowentFunction - Interface in flowent
FlowentFunction is a way of expressing a completely safe method, executable in the Flowent method chain using Flowent.runMethod(FlowentFunction).
FlowentWhileLoop - Interface in flowent
FlowentWhileLoop is an interface that can be utilized to create loops from within the method chain.
